       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    PSI79900.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA PSI79900.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Browse Detalhe
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI79900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDDET002 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV7990.
       COPY PSCV7991.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * Copy transforma??o de datas
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY AQCW0009.
       COPY AQCL0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCL0110.
       COPY ETCL0002.
      *     OBTEM NOME DO CLIENTE NA BANKA
       COPY PSCK0001.
       COPY PSCK0002.
       COPY SXCL0380.
       COPY SXCL0002.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAW0020.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY ETCL0188.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-2                       VALUE '2'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-3                       VALUE '3'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-4                       VALUE '3'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-PSDETALH PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSDETALH'.
           05 CON-PRG-NAME PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI79900'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI79900'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-VARIAVEIS.
          05 WS-NCLI                       PIC  9(09)        VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NCLI-MIN                   PIC S9(09) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NCLI-MAX                   PIC S9(09) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-DINT-MIN                   PIC S9(08) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-DINT-MAX                   PIC S9(08) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NFIC-MIN                   PIC S9(06) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NFIC-MAX                   PIC S9(06) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NREG-MIN                   PIC S9(06) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
          05 WS-NREG-MAX                   PIC S9(06) COMP-3 VALUE 0.
           05 WS-CNTA                   PIC  9(11) VALUE ZEROES.
           05 REDEFINES WS-CNTA.
              10 WS-CNTA-NCLI           PIC  9(08).
              10 WS-CNTA-NATR           PIC  9(02).
              10 WS-CNTA-NSEQ           PIC  9(01).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURPST01 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       DTNCLI
                     , DTDINT
                     , DTNFIC
                     , DTNREG
                     , DTREF
                     , DTTREG
                     , DTTOPE
                     , DTSITC
                     , DTSITR
                     , DTCBAN
                     , DTCBAL
                     , DTCNTA
                     , DTCDIG
                     , DTMONT
                     , DTNOME
                     , DTREFTR
                     , DTDVAL
                     , DTNTRY
                     , DTNOCB
                     , DTSITU
                     , DTMAIL
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEEST
                     , DTRALT
                     , DTNOMEB
                     , DTDDEB
                 FROM PSDETALHE2
                 WHERE ( DTNCLI  > :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                    OR  (DTNCLI  = :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                   AND   DTDINT  > :PSDETALHE-DTDINT)
                    OR  (DTNCLI  = :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                   AND   DTDINT  = :PSDETALHE-DTDINT
                   AND   DTNFIC  > :PSDETALHE-DTNFIC)
                    OR  (DTNCLI  = :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                   AND   DTDINT  = :PSDETALHE-DTDINT
                   AND   DTNFIC  = :PSDETALHE-DTNFIC
                   AND   DTNREG >= :PSDETALHE-DTNREG))
                   AND   DTNCLI <= :WS-NCLI-MAX
                   AND   DTNCLI >= :WS-NCLI-MIN
                   AND   DTDINT <= :WS-DINT-MAX
                   AND   DTDINT >= :WS-DINT-MIN
                   AND   DTNFIC <= :WS-NFIC-MAX
                   AND   DTNFIC >= :WS-NFIC-MIN
                   AND   DTNREG <= :WS-NREG-MAX
                   AND   DTNREG >= :WS-NREG-MIN
                 ORDER BY
                         DTNCLI
                       , DTDINT
                       , DTNFIC
                       , DTNREG
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI79900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '0000-MAINLINE.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV7990-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ASE               TO PSCV7991-ASE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNCLIF     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNCLIF       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNMCLI     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNMCLI       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORDINTF     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORDINTF       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNFICF     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNFICF       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNREGF     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(5)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNREGF       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNCLI      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(6)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORDINT      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(7)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORDINT        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(7)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNFIC      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(8)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNFIC        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(8)
              MOVE 'PSCV7990-ORNREG      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(9)
              MOVE  PSCV7990-ORNREG        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(9)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
              INITIALIZE VIAL0015-DATA
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCV7991-INDICE.
           PERFORM 1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
              THRU 1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL PSCV7991-PAGINA-CHEIA.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1100-LIMPA-OCCURS.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       MOVE '1100-LIMPA-OCCURS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.
      *
           ADD 1                       TO PSCV7991-INDICE.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNCLI(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNMCLI(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORDINT(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNFIC(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNREG(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCBAN(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCBAL(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCNTA(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCDIG(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORMONT(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOME(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOCB(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORDVAL(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORSITU(PSCV7991-INDICE)
      *
           .
       1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNCLIF           TO PSCV7991-ORNCLIF.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNMCLI           TO PSCV7991-ORNMCLI.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINTF           TO PSCV7991-ORDINTF.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINTF           TO PSCV7991-ORDINTF.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNFICF           TO PSCV7991-ORNFICF.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNREGF           TO PSCV7991-ORNREGF.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNCLI            TO PSCV7991-ORNCLI .
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINT            TO PSCV7991-ORDINT .
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINT            TO PSCV7991-ORDINT .
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNFIC            TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC .
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNREG            TO PSCV7991-ORNREG .
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORTSERV           TO PSCV7991-ORTSERV.
      *
           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
                 THRU 4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    COMPUTE PSCV7991-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         PSCV7991-INDICE-INVERSO * PSCV7991-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE PSCV7991-LENGTH EQUAL PSCV7991-LENGTH
                         - PSCV7991-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *             MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORNCLI-S
      *             MOVE PSCK0001-DTNCLI-N-EXISTS
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORNCLI-MSG
      *             MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORDINT-S
      *             MOVE PSCK0001-DTDINT-N-EXISTS
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-MSG
      *             MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORNREG-S
      *             MOVE PSCK0001-DTNREG-N-EXISTS
      *               TO PSCV7991-ORNREG-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '****-FIM-2000'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV7991-ORNMCLI'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV7991-ORNMCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0380-VERSAO
           MOVE CON-PRG-NAME               TO SXCL0380-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-NOME-CLI      TO SXCL0380-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0380-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0380-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0380-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0380-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0380-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0380-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG         TO SXCL0380-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL         TO SXCL0380-VNCR.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO SXCL0380-CLBAL.
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNCLI            TO SXCL0380-CLNCLI.

           CALL SXCL0380-ROTINA         USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                              SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE SXCL0380-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV7991-ORNCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS TO PSCV7991-ORNCLI-MSG
           ELSE
              MOVE SXCL0380-DWT OF SXCL0380-WT OF SXCL0380-DATA(1)
                                           TO PSCV7991-ORNMCLI
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '****-OBTEM-NOME-CLI'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV7991-ORNMCLI'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV7991-ORNMCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           CONTINUE.

       2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN.'            TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * TRATA CLIENTE
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNCLIF           TO PSDETALHE-DTNCLI.
           IF PSCV7990-ORNCLI  EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE 0                       TO WS-NCLI-MIN
              MOVE 999999999               TO WS-NCLI-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCV7990-ORNCLI         TO WS-NCLI-MIN
                                              WS-NCLI-MAX
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'TRATOU CLIENTE'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * TRATA DATA INTEGRACAO
           IF PSCV7990-ORDINTF   EQUAL SPACES OR VIAK0002-DATA-MINIMA
              MOVE 0                       TO PSDETALHE-DTDINT
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINTF        TO AQCW0005-DTX10
              PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
                 THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
              MOVE AQCW0005-DT98           TO PSDETALHE-DTDINT
           END-IF.
           IF PSCV7990-ORDINT   EQUAL SPACES OR VIAK0002-DATA-MINIMA
              MOVE 0                       TO WS-DINT-MIN
              MOVE 99999999                TO WS-DINT-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCV7990-ORDINT         TO AQCW0005-DTX10
              PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
                 THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
              MOVE AQCW0005-DT98           TO WS-DINT-MIN
                                              WS-DINT-MAX
           END-IF.

      * TRATA NRO FICHEIRO
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNFICF           TO PSDETALHE-DTNFIC.
           IF PSCV7990-ORNFIC  EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE 0                       TO WS-NFIC-MIN
              MOVE 999999                  TO WS-NFIC-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCV7990-ORNFIC         TO WS-NFIC-MIN
                                              WS-NFIC-MAX
           END-IF.

      * TRATA NRO DO REGISTO
           MOVE PSCV7990-ORNREGF           TO PSDETALHE-DTNREG.
      *    MOVE PSCV7990-ORNREG            TO PSDETALHE-DTNREG.
           IF PSCV7990-ORNREG   EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE PSCK0002-FCNREG-HEADER  TO WS-NREG-MIN
              MOVE PSCK0002-FCNREG-TRAILER TO WS-NREG-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCV7990-ORNREG         TO WS-NREG-MIN
                                              WS-NREG-MAX
           END-IF.

           SET SW-CURSOR-NONE              TO TRUE             .

           IF SW-CURSOR-NONE
              SET SW-CURSOR-1              TO TRUE
           END-IF.

           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                 IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
                    MOVE 'ANTES OPEN'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                    MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNFI' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                    MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNFIC TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                    MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNCL' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
                    MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNCLI TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
                    MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTDIN' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
                    MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTDINT TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
                    MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNFI' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
                    MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNFIC TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
                    MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNRE' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(5)
                    MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNREG TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
                    MOVE 'WS-NCLI        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(6)
                    MOVE  WS-NCLI-MIN      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
                    MOVE  WS-NCLI-MAX   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)(10:10)
                    MOVE 'WS-DINT        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(7)
                    MOVE  WS-DINT-MIN      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(7)
                    MOVE  WS-DINT-MAX   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(7)(10:10)
                    MOVE 'WS-NFIC        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(8)
                    MOVE  WS-NFIC-MIN      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(8)
                    MOVE  WS-NFIC-MAX   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(8)(10:10)
                    MOVE 'WS-NREG        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(9)
                    MOVE  WS-NREG-MIN      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(9)
                    MOVE  WS-NREG-MAX   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(9)(10:10)
                    PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                       THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 EXEC SQL
                    OPEN CURPST01
                 END-EXEC
           END-EVALUATE.

           MOVE CON-PSDETALH               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                    EXEC SQL
                       FETCH CURPST01
                       INTO
                           :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTDINT
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNFIC
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNREG
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTREF
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTTREG
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTTOPE
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTSITC
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTSITR
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTCBAN
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTCBAL
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTCNTA
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTCDIG
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTMONT
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNOME
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTREFTR
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTDVAL
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNTRY
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNOCB
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTSITU
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTMAIL
                         , :PSDETALHE-CUSERID
                         , :PSDETALHE-HTIMEEST
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTRALT
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB
                         , :PSDETALHE-DTDDEB
                    END-EXEC


           END-EVALUATE.

           MOVE CON-PSDETALH               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCV7991-INDICE.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
                OR PSCV7991-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT PSCV7991-PAGINA-CHEIA
                    COMPUTE PSCV7991-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                         PSCV7991-INDICE-INVERSO - PSCV7991-INDICE
                    COMPUTE PSCV7991-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         PSCV7991-INDICE-INVERSO * PSCV7991-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE PSCV7991-LENGTH EQUAL PSCV7991-LENGTH -
                         PSCV7991-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           ADD 1                       TO PSCV7991-INDICE.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2051-FORMATA-LISTA
                 THRU 2051-FORMATA-LISTA-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
AR0817* Se beneficiario OIC,o nome tem de estar preenchido
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS                         AND
              PSDETALHE-DTCBAN NOT EQUAL VIAL0001-CBANCO AND
              PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE) EQUAL
              PSCK0002-SITC-NORMAL
      *
              IF PSDETALHE-DTNOME EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE     PSCK0002-SITC-REF-TEI-INV
                   TO PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE)
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
      * Se beneficiario do banco e nome preenchido compara 2 nomes
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS                   AND
              PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB NOT EQUAL SPACES   AND
              PSDETALHE-DTCBAN      EQUAL VIAL0001-CBANCO
      *
              PERFORM 2053-COMPARA-NOME
                 THRU 2053-COMPARA-NOME-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2054-FORMATA-NOME
                 THRU 2054-FORMATA-NOME-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.
      *
       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2051-FORMATA-LISTA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2051-FORMATA-LISTA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2051-FORMATA-LISTA   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNCLI(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTDINT           TO AQCW0005-DT98
      *
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT.
      *
           MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORDINT(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNFIC
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNFIC(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNREG
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNREG(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTSITC
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAN
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCBAN(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAL
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCBAL(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCNTA
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCNTA(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCDIG
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORCDIG(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTMONT
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORMONT(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOME
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOME(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTDVAL           TO AQCW0005-DT98.
      *
                PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                   THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT       .
      *
           MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORDVAL(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOCB
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOCB(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTSITU
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORSITU(PSCV7991-INDICE).
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTRALT
             TO PSCV7991-D-ORRALT(PSCV7991-INDICE).
      *
       2051-FORMATA-LISTA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2053-COMPARA-NOME
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2053-COMPARA-NOME.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2053-COMPARA-NOME   '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTCNTA    '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTCNTA       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB   '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           INITIALIZE ARCL0110-DATA      REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO ARCL0110-AT-VERSAO.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO ARCL0110-USERC.
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCNTA           TO WS-CNTA       .
ES1010*    MOVE WS-CNTA-NCLI               TO ARCL0110-NCLI .
ES0110     PERFORM 4000-OBTEM-CONTA
ES0110        THRU 4000-OBTEM-CONTA-EXIT
ES0110     MOVE WS-NCLI                    TO ARCL0110-NCLI .
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB          TO ARCL0110-NOME .
      *
           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT.
      *
           PERFORM ARCP0110-COMPARA-NOMES
              THRU ARCP0110-COMPARA-NOMES-EXIT.
      *
           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2053-COMPARA-NOME '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCL0110-RCODE '       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  ARCL0110-RCODE         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'ARCL0110-NOME  '       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  ARCL0110-NOME          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'ARCL0110-NCLI  '       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  ARCL0110-NCLI          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-IND-ERROS '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-NR-ERRO   '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (5)
              MOVE  ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (6)
              MOVE  ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-RCODE          TO VIAW0020-RCODE

              PERFORM VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE
                 THRU VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS       TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              SET  PSCV7991-ORNFIC-1        TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO         TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-MSG
              MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO     TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-CAPLIC
           ELSE
              EVALUATE TRUE
                 WHEN  ARCL0110-RCODE EQUAL ARCK0002-RCODE-OK
                       CONTINUE
      *
                 WHEN  ARCL0110-RCODE EQUAL ARCK0002-RCODE-INF
                    IF PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE) EQUAL
                           PSCK0002-SITC-NORMAL
      *
                       MOVE PSCK0002-SITC-NOME-DIF TO
                        PSCV7991-D-ORSITC(PSCV7991-INDICE)
                    END-IF
      *
                 WHEN  OTHER
                    SET  VIAL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO TRUE
                    SET  PSCV7991-ORNFIC-1     TO TRUE
                    MOVE ARCK0001-ERR-VAL-NOME TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-MSG
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR    TO PSCV7991-ORNFIC-CAPLIC
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.
      *
       2053-COMPARA-NOME-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                2054-FORMATA-NOME
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2054-FORMATA-NOME.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2054-FORMATA-NOME   '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-CBANCO     '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-CBANCO        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTCBAN    '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTCBAN       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB   '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'PSDETALHE-DTNOME    '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNOME       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF PSDETALHE-DTCBAN      EQUAL VIAL0001-CBANCO AND
              PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB NOT EQUAL SPACES
      *
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB
                TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOME(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           ELSE
              MOVE  PSDETALHE-DTNOME
                TO PSCV7991-D-ORNOME(PSCV7991-INDICE)
           END-IF.
      *
       2054-FORMATA-NOME-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                    EXEC SQL
                        CLOSE CURPST01
                    END-EXEC
           END-EVALUATE.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV7991-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV7991-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV7991-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE PSCV7991-INDICE            TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
       4000-OBTEM-CONTA.
      ******************************************************************
      *
           INITIALIZE ETCL0188-DATA   REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                           ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES
      *
           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT

           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAN          TO ETCL0188-CDNIB-BANCO
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAL          TO ETCL0188-CDNIB-BALCAO
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCNTA          TO ETCL0188-CDNIB-CONTA
           MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCDIG          TO ETCL0188-CDNIB-CDIG

           SET  ETCL0188-CDTTR-CSCNT      TO TRUE

           CALL ETCL0188-ROTINA        USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                             ETCL0188-DATA.
      *
      * Se o NIB năo existir no BANKA, segue o percurso normal
      * do programa e formata o erro de cliente inexistente mais
      * ŕ frente, formata os dados da conta com a conta de input
      *
           IF NOT ETCL0002-RCODE-OK
              SET ETCL0002-RCODE-OK        TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDNIB-NCLI     TO WS-NCLI
      * Se estiver tudo bem, usa os dados da conta devolvidos
      * pela API
           ELSE
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDNCLI         TO WS-NCLI
           END-IF.
      *
       4000-OBTEM-CONTA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
       COPY AQCP0005.
       COPY AQCP0009.
       COPY ARCP0110.
       COPY ETCP0002.
       COPY VIAP0016.
       COPY VIAP0020.

